Enum AbstractCertificationItem.ContinuousState

  • java.lang.Object

    AbstractCertificationItem
    public static enum AbstractCertificationItem.ContinuousState
extends java.lang.Enum<AbstractCertificationItem.ContinuousState>
implements sailpoint.tools.Localizable
    An enumeration of possible continuous certification states that indicate the timeliness of certification for an AbstractCertificationItem.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant Description
      CertificationRequired
      The item is in need recertification soon.
      Certified
      The item has been certified and does not currently need recertification.
      Overdue
      The item is overdue for recertification.
